1. Blockchain Forks Kya Hai?
Blockchain mein "Fork" ka matlab hai jab ek purani blockchain split (do hisson mein batna) ho jati hai taaki naye niyam (rules) lagu kiye ja sakein.

Naye Rules: Jab purane blockchain network mein kuch badlav karne hote hain, toh blockchain ko "split" karke ek nayi chain banayi jati hai jo naye niyam follow karti hai.
Chain Split: Image mein dikhaya gaya hai ki kaise Block 1, Block 2, aur Block 3 ek line mein jude hain. Fork hone par isi line se ek nayi raah nikal jati hai.

Forks ke Mukhya Fayde (Wallets ke sandarbh mein):
1. Hardware aur Paper wallets ka ek bada fayda ye hai ki inme Forks ke doran milne wale naye coins ko claim karna bahut aasaan hota hai.

2. Free Coins: Jab koi bada fork hota hai (jaise Bitcoin se Bitcoin Cash bana tha), toh aksar purane holders ko naye blockchain par utne hi naye coins free mein milte hain.

3. Control: Kyunki aapke paas apni "Private Keys" ka poora control hota hai, isliye aap in naye coins ke malik hote hain.


